  IF par_isoc EQ 'X'.                  "ISO Code
    PERFORM isocode_umsetzen USING reguh-waers regud-waers.
  ELSE.
    regud-waers = reguh-waers.
  ENDIF.

* Ländername des Zahlungsempfängers lesen ------------------------------
