* Buchungsdatum des Zahlungsbelegs (in Worten) -------------------------
* posting date of payment document (in words) --------------------------
  SELECT SINGLE * FROM t015m
    WHERE spras EQ hlp_sprache
    AND   monum EQ reguh-zaldt+4(2).
  IF sy-subrc EQ 0.
